git push --force   # dangerous on shared branches
```

### âœ… Correct fix

```bash
git revert <bad-commit-hash>
git push
```

History stays safe.

---

## ğŸ§¨ Scenario 5: â€œBranch is behind mainâ€

### â— Problem

PR shows conflicts because `main` moved on.

### ğŸ” Diagnose

```bash
git fetch origin
git log --oneline --decorate --all --graph
```

### âœ… Fix (merge approach)

```bash
git switch feature
git merge origin/main
```

Or (cleaner history):

```bash
git rebase origin/main
```

